    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="-en-paragraph:true;"><font style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">Note: The two histologically similar tumors are within 5.0 mm of each other, the size is measured from outer edges of the two.</font></span></div></en-note>      ]]>
